{"id": 61184, "date": "2025-10-22T04:00:16", "date_gmt": "2025-10-22T11:00:16", "guid": {"rendered": "https://estreetshuffle.com/?p=61184"}, "modified": "2026-06-28T13:52:10", "modified_gmt": "2026-06-28T20:52:10", "slug": "kingdom-of-days-october-22-2", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/10/22/kingdom-of-days-october-22-2/", "title": {"rendered": "October 22"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p><strong>1976: </strong>Bruce drops by The Hanger in Hazlet, New Jersey, to see Gary U.S. Bonds perform&#8211;unknown to Gary. Mid-show, the owner whispers to Gary that Bruce is in the audience and is interested in joining him on stage. Gary has no idea who Bruce is, but his band does and they encourage Bonds to say yes. He does, and Bruce and Gary meet for the first time. Bruce borrows a guitar and plays with Bonds and the band for about an hour, and afterwards Bruce invites Gary to join him at his show at the Palladium the following week.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"5092\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1976-1022/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?fit=1086%2C684&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"1086,684\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1976-1022\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?fit=758%2C477&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-5092 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?resize=758%2C477&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?w=1086&amp;ssl=1 1086w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?resize=300%2C189&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?resize=768%2C484&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/1976-1022.jpg?resize=1024%2C645&amp;ssl=1 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1984:\u00a0</strong>At their second of two nights at the Oakland Coliseum on the Born in the U.S.A. Tour, Bruce and the band tour premiere &#8220;Stolen Car&#8221; and play their first-ever performance of &#8220;Shut Out the Light.&#8221; Bruce brings his sister Pam on stage for &#8220;Dancing in the Dark.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-NN0O68Cw-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/NN0O68Cw?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=PLJTyL9twk3zB33eyP6HMctOXaEcrYQa9_\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"30304\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-10-22-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?fit=795%2C1760&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"795,1760\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-10-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?fit=463%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-30304 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?resize=758%2C1678&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1678\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?w=795&amp;ssl=1 795w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?resize=136%2C300&amp;ssl=1 136w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?resize=463%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 463w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?resize=768%2C1700&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1984-10-22.png?resize=694%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 694w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"22073\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1984-10-22a/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?fit=930%2C1124&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"930,1124\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1984-10-22a\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?fit=758%2C916&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-22073 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?resize=758%2C916&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"916\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?w=930&amp;ssl=1 930w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?resize=248%2C300&amp;ssl=1 248w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?resize=847%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 847w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1984-10-22a.png?resize=768%2C928&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>1992:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and his new band play their second of two nights at Mountain View&#8217;s Shoreline Amphitheater, featuring the last performance to date of &#8220;The Long Goodbye.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/pLyZ1hHJHd8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>1996:\u00a0</strong>Bruce plays a solo acoustic show at the Civic Theater in San Diego.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/df5JHctwzsQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"30306\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/1996-10-22-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?fit=803%2C1405&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"803,1405\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"1996-10-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?fit=585%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-30306 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?resize=758%2C1326&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1326\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?w=803&amp;ssl=1 803w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?resize=171%2C300&amp;ssl=1 171w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?resize=585%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 585w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/1996-10-22.png?resize=768%2C1344&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2002:</strong>\u00a0Bruce tour premieres &#8220;The River&#8221; in a new solo guitar arrangement at his Rising Tour stop in Rotterdam. &#8220;Countin&#8217; on a Miracle&#8221; also receives a new arrangement, with Nils debuting a beautiful new acoustic introduction.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ajedDx-Bi3c?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Hj71uBv9V8k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/0sj9eO-6KDs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2006:\u00a0</strong>When the Seeger Sessions Tour comes to Granada, Bruce opens the encores with a tour debut, an acoustic &#8220;The Promised Land.&#8221;</p>\n<div id=\"v-buHbTTAH-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='604' src='https://videopress.com/embed/buHbTTAH?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div id=\"v-R0FIdYUv-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/R0FIdYUv?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ch7OXyP_JFw?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2007:\u00a0</strong>At Night Two in Chicago on the Magic Tour, &#8220;Tunnel of Love,&#8221; &#8220;Spirit in the Night,&#8221; and &#8221; &#8220;Thunder Road&#8221; make their tour debuts.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eFWOEkB44lI?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YNJyEjbmNwk?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2011:\u00a0</strong>Bruce (along with Roy, Max, Bobby Bandiera&#8217;s band and a horn section) plays a benefit show for Boston College at The Stone Pony in Asbury Park, featuring Bruce&#8217;s first &#8220;A Woman&#8217;s Got the Power&#8221; in 27 years.</p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"13648\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2011-10-22/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2011-10-22.jpg?fit=500%2C375&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"500,375\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2011-10-22\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2011-10-22.jpg?fit=500%2C375&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13648 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2011-10-22.jpg?resize=500%2C375&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2011-10-22.jpg?w=500&amp;ssl=1 500w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/2011-10-22.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2020: </strong>It&#8217;s the day before the release of Bruce&#8217;s latest album, and the virtual publicity tour is in full swing. This morning, E Street Radio airs Episode 4 of\u00a0<em>Letter to You Radio</em>, featuring a conversation between Bruce and Jon Stewart.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61184-36\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-22-LTY-Radio-4-Bruce-Jon-Stewart-1.mp3?_=36\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-22-LTY-Radio-4-Bruce-Jon-Stewart-1.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/2020-10-22-LTY-Radio-4-Bruce-Jon-Stewart-1.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>Also today, NPR airs an interview with Bruce.</p>\n<audio class=\"wp-audio-shortcode\" id=\"audio-61184-37\" preload=\"none\" style=\"width: 100%;\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"audio/mpeg\" src=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20201023_me_what_bruce_springsteen_lost_and_found.mp3?_=37\" /><a href=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20201023_me_what_bruce_springsteen_lost_and_found.mp3\">https://estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/20201023_me_what_bruce_springsteen_lost_and_found.mp3</a></audio>\n<p>Finally, Apple TV+ releases the <em>Letter to You </em>documentary film, featuring Bruce and E Street Band recording their new album.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/FLHv-ia1M6Y?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>And in the last hour before Release Day, Apple Music&#8217;s Zane Lowe interviews Bruce and moderates questions from fans in a <em>New Music Daily</em> special event.</p>\n<div id=\"v-MGsbgB6v-1\" class=\"video-player\"><iframe title='VideoPress Video Player' aria-label='VideoPress Video Player' width='758' height='426' src='https://videopress.com/embed/MGsbgB6v?hd=1&amp;cover=1&amp;loop=0&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;permalink=1&amp;muted=0&amp;controls=1&amp;playsinline=0&amp;useAverageColor=0&amp;preloadContent=metadata' frameborder='0' allowfullscreen data-resize-to-parent=\"true\" allow='clipboard-write'></iframe><script data-jetpack-boost=\"ignore\" src='https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/plugins/video/assets/js/next/videopress-iframe.js'></script></div>\n<p><strong>2024:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band rehearse at Sirius XM Studio in New York City for their appearance on\u00a0<em>The Howard Stern Show\u00a0</em>the following day.</p>\n<p><strong>2025:</strong> Bruce attends and performs at AFI fest&#8217;s screening of <em>Springsteen: Deliver Me From Nowhere</em> at TCL Chinese Theater in Los Angeles.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/qycpaElNUys?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4T9mj0DF9_k?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtub